gacy.JDOQLQuery.getParsedImports(JDOQLQuery.java:364)\n\tat org.datanucleus.store.rdbms.query.legacy.JDOQLQuery.compileInternal(JDOQLQuery.java:174)\n\tat org.datanucleus.store.query.Query.executeQuery(Query.java:1628)\n\tat org.datanucleus.store.rdbms.query.legacy.JDOQLQuery.executeQuery(JDOQLQuery.java:245)\n\tat org.datanucleus.store.query.Query.executeWithArray(Query.java:1499)\n\tat org.datanucleus.jdo.JDOQuery.execute(JDOQuery.java:243)\n\tat org.apache.hadoop.hive.metastore.ObjectStore.getMDatabase(ObjectStore.java:389)\n\tat org.apache.hadoop.hive.metastore.ObjectStore.getDatabase(ObjectStore.java:408)\n\tat sun.reflect.NativeMethodAccessorImpl.invoke0(Native Method)\n         ...\n         ...\n         at $Proxy0.getDatabase(Unknown Source)\n\tat org.apache.hadoop.hive.metastore.HiveMetaStore$HMSHandler.createDefaultDB_core(HiveMetaStore.java:351)\n\tat org.apache.hadoop.hive.metastore.HiveMetaStore$HMSHandler.createDefaultDB(HiveMetaStore.java:375)\n\tat org.apache.hadoop.hive.metastore.HiveMetaStore$HMSHandler.init(HiveMetaStore.java:278)  \n{noformat}","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=rohithsharma","name":"rohithsharma","key":"rohithsharma","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Rohith Sharma K S","active":true,"timeZone":"Australia/Sydney"},"created":"2012-09-15T09:04:05.755+0000","updated":"2012-09-15T09:04:05.755+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12607753/comment/13456357","id":"13456357","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=rohithsharma","name":"rohithsharma","key":"rohithsharma","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Rohith Sharma K S","active":true,"timeZone":"Australia/Sydney"},"body":"Any exception in above 1 or 3, Hive client hangs forever.\n\nIf we synchronize Metastore.createDefaultDB_core(), all the 3 problem can be resolved. Please suggest your opinion..","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=rohithsharma","name":"rohithsharma","key":"rohithsharma","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Rohith Sharma K S","active":true,"timeZone":"Australia/Sydney"},"created":"2012-09-15T09:09:48.302+0000","updated":"2012-09-15T09:09:48.302+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12607753/comment/13457216","id":"13457216","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=cwsteinbach","name":"cwsteinbach","key":"cwsteinbach","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Carl Steinbach","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"body":"It looks like createDefaultDB() (which calls createDefaultDB_core()) is already synchronized. Any idea why this doesn't solve the problem?","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=cwsteinbach","name":"cwsteinbach","key":"cwsteinbach","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Carl Steinbach","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"created":"2012-09-17T18:44:17.922+0000","updated":"2012-09-17T18:44:17.922+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12607753/comment/13457605","id":"13457605","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=rohithsharma","name":"rohithsharma","key":"rohithsharma","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Rohith Sharma K S","active":true,"timeZone":"Australia/Sydney"},"body":"bq. Any idea why this doesn't solve the problem?\nI am using hive branch-0.9.0. The above problem is fixed in Hive-Trunk only.\n\nI gone through the hive-trunk code for the above problem. I have one doubt on the synchronization,\nExact synchronization problem exist on method createDefaultDB_core(). Why it is synchronized for calling method createDefaultDB().?\n\nCorrect me If I am wrong, synchronizing calling method impact would be on getting client connection is delayed. There is \"if\" block in method \"createDefaultDB()\"  that check for flag \"createDefaultDB\". Synchronizing to this method lead execute this if check only one client. This if check we can do parallel by bringing down synchronization one layer to the method createDefaultDB_core().\n","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=rohithsharma","name":"rohithsharma","key":"rohithsharma","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Rohith Sharma K S","active":true,"timeZone":"Australia/Sydney"},"created":"2012-09-18T05:07:13.219+0000","updated":"2012-09-18T05:07:13.219+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12607753/comment/13458001","id":"13458001","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=cwsteinbach","name":"cwsteinbach","key":"cwsteinbach","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Carl Steinbach","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"body":"@Rohit: We could probably adjust the layering of these two methods slightly, but I doubt that it would accomplish much in terms of improving performance, mainly because this operation is done once per connection, and we expect clients to spend most of their time doing something else. If HIVE-2937 fixes the concurrency issue then I think we should probably mark this ticket as a duplicate of 2937 and backport 2937 to 0.9.","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=cwsteinbach","name":"cwsteinbach","key":"cwsteinbach","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Carl Steinbach","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"created":"2012-09-18T17:57:34.523+0000","updated":"2012-09-18T17:57:34.523+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12607753/comment/13461604","id":"13461604","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=rohithsharma","name":"rohithsharma","key":"rohithsharma","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Rohith Sharma K S","active":true,"timeZone":"Australia/Sydney"},"body":"Applying patch of HIVE-2937 has fixed all 3 issue as per description. This we can mark as duplicate of 2937.","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=rohithsharma","name":"rohithsharma","key":"rohithsharma","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Rohith Sharma K S","active":true,"timeZone":"Australia/Sydney"},"created":"2012-09-24T05:16:51.403+0000","updated":"2012-09-24T05:16:51.403+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12607753/comment/13461618","id":"13461618","author":{"self":"https